{"tid":740672,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"澳洲女性導演將為漫威執導「黑寡婦」獨立電影","createTime":"2018-07-13T05:15:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-16T05:03:35.000Z","uid":41343,"like":6,"dislike":77,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"911cd43492bb8de40f28e570f41a1dd24955bb0f","tid":740672,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T05:15:52.000Z","msg":"漫威影業的「黑寡婦」獨立電影終於選定了導演人選，澳洲出身的49歲女性導演凱特蕭蘭（Cate Shortland）將執導這部由史嘉蕾喬韓森（Scarlett Johansson）主演的作品。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n根據美國媒體報導，為了替這部電影尋找理想的導演人選，漫威影業花了超過半年的時間與超過70名導演洽談，其中「女性」是他們的優先條件，只有在挑選工作陷入困頓的時候，漫威影業才會考慮男性導演。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n台灣觀眾或許對凱特蕭蘭不太熟悉，但她早在2004年就以電影《我行我愛》（Somersault）在澳洲影視藝術學院獎（Australian Film Institute Awards）獲得最佳影片、最佳導演和最佳女主角等13項大獎，並入圍該年坎城影展「一種注目」單元，獲得國際影壇注目，去年她的第三部劇情長片《顫慄柏林》（Berlin Syndrome）曾在台灣院線上映。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n《雪寶的佳節冒險》女性編劇賈克沙弗（Jac Schaeffer）為這部電影執筆最新一版的劇本，《黑寡婦》目前檔期未定，它將會是繼《驚奇隊長》之後，漫威影業第二部以女性為主角的超級英雄電影，由布麗拉森（Brie Larson）主演的《驚奇隊長》日前已經殺青，預計將2019年3月8日在北美上映。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.upmedia.mg/news_info.php?SerialNo=44446\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.upmedia.mg%2Fnews_info.php%3FSerialNo%3D44446&d=D2YYfmw9pscn5chN2XgR%2Bk%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=587df55d\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.upmedia.mg/news_info.php?SerialNo=44446</a>"},{"pid":"922fc460317bf11d3002b8171c2b80b553b09883","tid":740672,"uid":40272,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T05:23:36.000Z","msg":"咸片？"},{"pid":"2c88f180631089f9a3d1ac57aac123d052d81c6c","tid":740672,"uid":132587,"like":119,"dislike":6,"score":113,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T05:32:03.000Z","msg":"過曬氣 個樣殘曬先黎拍<br />\n早幾年拍就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nAvengers2之後就最perfect 套戲中間d幻覺當伏線"},{"pid":"522bbbaed51b633a04b18827915a05c9a10d6ab9","tid":740672,"uid":54959,"like":108,"dislike":4,"score":104,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T05:34:24.000Z","msg":"根據美國媒體報導，為了替這部電影尋找理想的導演人選，漫威影業花了超過半年的時間與超過70名導演洽談，其中「女性」是他們的優先條件，只有在挑選工作陷入困頓的時候，漫威影業才會考慮男性導演。<br />\n<br />\n工作崗位性別歧視喎"},{"pid":"7322165db0ed669fbc87b040bcdf984f2bb23e4f","tid":740672,"uid":27850,"like":50,"dislike":2,"score":48,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T05:36:16.000Z","msg":"feel到會變女權左膠戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a819a1c218df81b4b5d5ea3301d3bd7443273cb1","tid":740672,"uid":6261,"like":12,"dislike":4,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T05:59:21.000Z","msg":"逆向歧視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b414d729f298a9481d1848635795dd0f55f38f8c","tid":740672,"uid":125728,"like":60,"dislike":2,"score":58,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T07:12:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"185d6ecf1d8fbff0fe6c31fa6590d3136f78cc9e","tid":740672,"uid":41343,"like":1,"dislike":16,"score":-15,"quote":{"pid":"b414d729f298a9481d1848635795dd0f55f38f8c","tid":740672,"uid":125728,"like":60,"dislike":2,"score":58,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T07:12:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T07:15:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://digitalspyuk.cdnds.net/18/10/480x240/landscape-1520225504-frances-mcdormand-inclusion-rider.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdigitalspyuk.cdnds.net%2F18%2F10%2F480x240%2Flandscape-1520225504-frances-mcdormand-inclusion-rider.gif&h=b81c0842&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://shawetcanada.files.wordpress.com/2018/03/giphy.gif?w=480&amp;h=247&amp;crop=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fshawetcanada.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F03%2Fgiphy.gif%3Fw%3D480%26h%3D247%26crop%3D1&h=44026b42&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fc46054a81c2e5c8c2444406f6c9616b0fd08d45","tid":740672,"uid":118154,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"7322165db0ed669fbc87b040bcdf984f2bb23e4f","tid":740672,"uid":27850,"like":50,"dislike":2,"score":48,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T05:36:16.000Z","msg":"feel到會變女權左膠戲<img src=\"/assets/face